	* tests/t1700-probe-fs.sh: Rename from ...
	* tests/t1700-ext-probe.sh: ...this.
	* tests/Makefile.am (TESTS): Rename it here, too.

2011-02-26  Jiro SEKIBA  <jir@unicus.jp>

	libparted: add nilfs2 module
