	* tests/test-lib.sh: Don't use test's -a option.

	maint: remove empty lines at end of file
	This lets one more "syntax-check" test pass.
	Run this command:
	  git ls-files|grep -v gnulib|xargs perl -pi -0777 -e 's/\n\n+$/\n/'

